attacks.name: Surprise Attack
attacks.effect: Flip a coin. If tails, this attack does nothing.

attacks.name: Tropical Shake
attacks.effect: This attack does 20 more damage for each type of basic Energy card in your discard pile. You can’t add more than 100 damage in this way.

attacks.name: Controlled Burn
attacks.effect: Discard the top card of your opponent’s deck.

attacks.name: Flamethrower
attacks.effect: Discard an Energy from this Pokémon.

attacks.name: Fury Swipes
attacks.effect: Flip 3 coins. This attack does 10 damage for each heads.

attacks.name: Aqua Bullet
attacks.effect: This attack does 20 damage to 1 of your opponent’s Benched Pokémon. (Don’t apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

attacks.name: Hydro Pump
attacks.effect: This attack does 10 more damage times the amount of Water Energy attached to this Pokémon.

attacks.name: Iron Tail
attacks.effect: Flip a coin until you get tails. This attack does 20 damage for each heads.

attacks.name: Ominous Eyes
attacks.effect: Put 1 damage counter on 1 of your opponent’s Pokémon.

attacks.name: Three-Step Strike
attacks.effect: Flip 3 coins. This attack does 10 damage for each heads.

attacks.name: Screech
attacks.effect: During your next turn, the Defending Pokémon takes 20 more damage from attacks (after applying Weakness and Resistance).

attacks.name: Rage
attacks.effect: This attack does 10 more damage for each damage counter on this Pokémon.

attacks.name: Spoil the Fun
attacks.effect: If you go second, this attack does 60 more damage during your first turn.

attacks.name: Gold Rush
attacks.effect: Discard any number of Metal Energy cards from your hand. This attack does 30 damage for each card you discarded in this way.
